thread.title: Coulter to Trump: Get Back to Immigration, Trade, Infrastructure, Building a Wall — Not Paul Ryan’s ‘Standard GOP Corporatist Stuff’
thread.title_full: Coulter to Trump: Get Back to Immigration, Trade, Infrastructure, Building a Wall — Not Paul Ryan’s ‘Standard GOP Corporatist Stuff’

author: Jeff Poor
title: Coulter to Trump: Get Back to Immigration, Trade, Infrastructure, Building a Wall — Not Paul Ryan’s ‘Standard GOP Corporatist Stuff’
text: Wednesday on Fox News Channel's "Tucker Carlson Tonight," conservative commentator Ann Coulter, author of In Trump We Trust: E Pluribus Awesome!, echoed her call urging President Donald Trump to get back on track on fulfilling his campaign promises and spend less time on "Paul Ryan's priorities."
